{"tid":379750,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"港珠澳大橋建議","createTime":"2017-08-29T14:58:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T23:30:16.000Z","uid":70892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6c0a154376f693f3af6c925c56e1e0c7f22addbf","tid":379750,"uid":70892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T14:58:39.000Z","msg":"睇啲評論都話：啲私家車會塞爆座橋，或澳門咁細  邊有位泊咁多私家車，又或撞車邊個負責咁。<br />\n<br />\n建議：私家車只比有兩地牌既車通過。然後整啲專用黎過橋既大型巴士，負責送平民過橋，咁會唔會更有效使用港珠澳大橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7361bc010a788bff166a16f7d17c8eeb429e197","tid":379750,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T23:30:16.000Z","msg":"哇 多謝晒你個建議<br />\n你唔講真係無人諗到<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hk01.com/article/112017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F112017&d=YOVUTJKCNKRQH9lb%2FzAM%2F26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=ca24c007\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk01.com/article/112017</a>"}]}